illac.\nTh LaSalle is manufactured by\nthe adillac Motor or company en\ntirely within its own plants, and em\nbodies the same high qualities of\nworkmanship and standards of per\ntormance that are typical of the\nCadillac.\nUnder the d.rection of H. .M\nStephens, g.nernl sales manager, and\nNicholas Dreystadt. general service\nmanager, preparations were carried\non and completed for the rendering\nof prompt and efficient service in\nany locality, entirely in advance of\nthe introduction.\nAccording to the announcement,\nreserve supplies of spare parts are'\nalready held in every distributing\nrenter, in Case there may be need ol j\naccident replacements. Mechanics in 1\nevery pail of the country have been\ncarefully instructed so they are i\nthoroughly familiar with every fea- 1\nlure of the new car.\nA well-tmined force of service\nrepresentatives have, during the past j\nMonths, visited every distributing\ncenter instructing theXvarious main-\nti nance managers :s to the approved j\nmethods of servicing the lurSalle.\nThe announcement also \u00bbl:\u00abtes that i\nall tools necessary to perform o.a.n- J\ntenanee operations on the n**w car'\nwith complete instructions as to\nthtir use. ar.\u2019 already in the hands;\nof the service organisations of the j\ndistributors and d alers.\nBecause the new engine is a 99\ndegree, V-type eight and embodu\u00ab\nthe same fundamental prinripl* as\n1\nBearing\nCrankshaft\nI I\niliililili 1'j'l til 'll \"I wr VW^ir-'* 'IjWJfji \u2019ll\nChrviler \u201c60\u201d prices\u2014\nTouring Car,$1075;\nClub-^Coupe, $1125;\nCoach,$ 1145; Roadster,\n(w ith Rumble Seat),\n$1175; Coupe, (uith\nRumble Scat), $1245;\nSedan, $1245.\nF. O. B. Detroit, subject to\ncut rent Federal cjuut tax.\n'He-s,\nAll Chrysler cars are pro\ntected against theft under\nthe Fedco system. Chry\nsler dealers arc in position\nto extend the im\u00ab<cntence of\ntime payments. Asi about\nChrysler\u2019* attractive plan.\n4\nOF course, Chrysler \u201c60*\u2019 has a\nse ven* bear mg cranks h a ft.\nFor every six-cylinder Chrysler, since\nthe first Chrysler three years ago, has\na seven-bearing crankshaft, which\nmeans so much in smoother perform\nance and longer life.\nBesides, Chrysler \u201c60\u2019 has other ad\nmitted superiorities whose combina\ntion is found in no other car at its price.\nSpeed of 60 miles r us dash of 5 to\n25 miles in 7 /4 seconds, economy of\n22 miles to the gallon;*\nI mpuise neutralizer, full pressure lubri\ncation, oil-filter, air-cleaner;\nHydraulic four-wheel brakes, extraor\ndinary handling facility, road level\nlers for greater riding smoothness,\nlowness of chassis design, character\nistic Chrysler smartness of line,\nluxury of mohair upholstering, strik\ning colors.\nHere are reasons aplenty for Chrysler\n4\u201860V\u2019 sensational sales success, re\nflected in Chryslcr\u2019s dramatic rise from\n27th to 4th place.\nI\n815 COACH\nD_LTA MOTOR SALES\nSt. Charles and Fifth Street\nPhone 263\nI\nthat used in the Cadillac for the\npast 13 years, manitenanre men, be- j\ncause of their past training, are\neven brtter prepared to give efficient\nservice on the LaSalle.\nAccording to Mr. Dreystadt, the\nfame high standard of maintenance,\nwhich has always been characteristic\nof the Cadillac, will ope rat to its\nfullest extent with regard to the\nnew product. Contrary to the usual\nprocedure, the maintenance ot \u00bbd-\niliac cars is an integral part of the\nactiviti x of the -ales division. The\ncompany maintains that the Cadillac\nor La Salle owner hus not only pu:- j\nchased a car but is entitled to the\nmost highly satisfactory transpor\ntation service at all inies. Because\nit is expected that a great many La\nSails sales will be made to persons\nwho are already Cadillac owners, and\nbecause many more contacts art.\nmade with owners through service\nthan in cny other way. the recogni\ntion of this obligation as a sales ac-\ntivitv js regard'd by the company to\nbe of extreme importance.\ni\nScn^s After Dinner\nWill Be French Fad\nPARIS, March 19. A new com- j\nbination of wine, woman, and song\nthat has a beneficial influence in- j\nstead of the traditional harmful one.\nhas been advocated by Mrr.e. Beatrix\nDussane, one of the stars of the\nComedie-Franchise.\nMine. Dussane suggests that wo- I\nmen revive the old-fashioned French\ncustom of after dinner singing\naround the table, mak? it their new- j\nest fad and let it take the place of j\nsmoking Fhe considers that com- i\nbilled with the drinking of wine, th.s\nwill be an aid to digestion and good\ncheer. Mme. Dussane. although in\nmost things very fashionable still\nhas urbohbed golden hair and never\nsmokes.\nOUTLOOK FORl\nSPRING GOOD\nChevrolet Co. Optimis\ntic Over Business\nConditions\nAn optimist.;* note on the spring\nbusiness outlook in th automobile\nindustry, d mounting the \u2018saturation\npo nt' bugaboo ar.d pointing out fav\norable conditions throughout the\ncountry, is sounded tn a statement i\njust issued by Wiliam S. Knudsen,\nPresident and General Manager of\nthe Chevrolet Motor Company.\n\u201cIn forecasting a continuance of\ngood business prospects for the j\nSpring months, 1 am perhaps influ- t\nence.i by the aspect of our own >al/\nwhich have never been better in the 1\nhistory of th; company,\" said Mr.\nKnudsen.\n\u201cAs evidencing steady growth in\nautomobile production during this\nperiod, statistics issue! by the Unit\ned States Department of Commerce\nfor thi !;ui three year; covering th#\nsix months from January 1 to June\ndO are interesting. The figures for\nthese years follow:\nlt34 2.054.561\n11*25 2,173.525\n1*26 2,450,780\n\u201cWith these figures showing bus\nines: on the upgrud g nerally, there\nare only two rea-ons which could he\nadvanced for a possible decrease in.\nsales \u2014fir.it, reaching the so-called\n\u2018saturation point\u2019\u2014and second, a gen\nCtrl decline in business producing a\nreactive tendency jn buying\n\"No one has ever been able to ad\nvane* my reasonable fotinuU for\nfiguring the \u2018saturation point.\u2019 The\n'two or more' car trend is so pro\nnounced that former theories are be\ning constantly upset. If we knew\nthe total area which would be oc\ncupied if all cars produced were run\nning within that area, making it\nimpossible for this space to accom\nmodate any more cars, some basis\nwould be available for figuring 'sat\nuration-' But such u situation if\nimpossible\u2014and we may leave the\n\u25a0saturation point\u2019 for th:* future to\ndetermine, inasmuch as the humar\nmind will find it possible to open\nup any bottle-neck of traffic con\ngestion which might develop.\n\u201cAs for the general trend in bus\niness. country-wid? reports show the\nusual si ring activi*\u00bb is opening-up\ntwenty days ahead- of schedule. Wit!\nthe winter fairly mjld. marked onl*\nby severity in spots, rapid accelera\ntion of municipal and private con\nstruction operations is indicated.\nFarming should start early due to\nthe good weather and manfacturing\noperations generally are in excellent\ncondition.\n\u201cRapid turnover at smaller prof\nits is the keynote throughout indus\ntry as reflected by our country\u2019s bus\niness. With this policy can only\ncome a demand for more transporta\ntion.\n\"The shippers are demanding bet\nter freight service; the business\ntraveller is demanding better train\nseivice and the automobile user is\ndemanding better service of his car.\nsmf the firm that is in a position\nto assure the buyer this better serv\ni e can have nothing but bright pros\nr\u00bbects for the spring of 1827.\u201d\nANT1-REI) CAMPAIGN M\nLEEDS. Eng -More than 1.000 e>\n\u2022flieor of army arul navy have beenV\n\u25a0nlisteil for u year's campaign of\n\u25a0ratory against Communism in\n.r at Britain.\nDo >ge Brothers\nMotor Car\nthat Draw Crowds\nand Sivatj Buyers\nLittle wonder Dodge Brothers Motor Cars\ntoday are accorded such widespread and\nenthusiastic commendation\u2014\nSmart new body lines and attractive color\ncombinations\u2014\nA new seating arrangement that provides\nstill more roominess and comfort\u2014\nA new clutch, simple, sure, silent\u2014\nSofter pedal action, easier gear shifting\u2014\nQuicker acceleration, still greater steer\ning ease\u2014\nMore rigid engine support\u2014and smoother\nperformance\u2014\nNew, silent-type muffler\u2014\nSturdiness and dependability made still\nmore pronounced by vital betterments in\nbody construction and in the propeller\nshaft, differential and axle shafts.\nAdd to these the new five-bearing chrome\nvanadium crankshaft, with its remarkable\nimprovement in engine performance, the\nexcellent new starting and lighting system\nand many other recent betterments, and\nyou understand why owners proclaim\ntoday\u2019s car\u2014\n\u201cThe finest Dodge ever built!\u201d\nStandard Sedan.$1060.00\nSpecial Sedan.$1160.00\nDcLuxe Sedan.$1285.00\nDelivered\nJESSE DENNETT, Inc.\n1208 Elizabeth Brownsville\nWe Alao Sell Dependable Used Cara _\n\nJ","height":"36396","width":"28324"}}
